<hr />
I am a musician and have a band web site and would love to have a board up like this eventually. I used to have a guestbook, but I was forced to discontinue it because of spamers loading html codes into my guestbook that would lead you straight to their porn site. Very annoying! So I took the guestbook out. 
<br />

<br />
But a board like this can be a lot of fun. Especially it can give me reactions to my performances, cds, etc.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, does it take a lot of effort to maintain it? I don't have much time on my hands...
<br />

<br />
