<td valign="top" class="postbody">
<hr />
No, it really isn't hard to maintain.  I've only had a few spam messages pop up here, and if I don't have time to catch it I know one of the fantastic moderators would delete it for me  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Setup is really easy too.  Basically you just have to upload all the files and change the configuration (look and feel stuff).  This board is run with phpBB2...here's the link:  <a href="http://www.phpbb.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://www.phpbb.com</a>.  I've been reading about the next version, and it sounds like they're going to be adding a lot of cool features.  I'm not sure when it's being released though, I've been reading all sorts of rumors.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and if you would have any trouble installing a message board on your site, I'm sure someone here could help out with questions  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /></td>
</tr>
