<td valign="top" class="postbody">
<hr />
There are also some Guestbook updates out there now that have gotten better at killing out spammers.
<br />

<br />
I'm working on setting up my family genealogy site now.  I'm attempting to learn how to use PHP Nuke to set it up.  PHP Nuke is a full throttle database driven modular programming tool.  It allows you to set up your website structure and then all you do is update content modules.  You can change various pieces of info easily (so they say) and your content gets updated without having to do a bunch of programming.  We'll see...  it also has a forum module which installs phpBB as a part of the site.  I may eventually use it.
<br />

<br />
With all the php based stuff, the biggest challenge is editing the underlying code to add things like your personal logo and such.  Thankfully, you usually only have to do that once.</td>
