<hr />
And I almost forgot...
<br />

<br />
I've been pretty happy with the guestbook I've been using.  I got LOTS of spam with my old one, but so far I've had very little with this one.  Plus, I have it set so I can approve the entries before they show up.  So if I do get any spam messages (I think I've only had 2 the past few months), I just delete them instead of approving them, and they never show up for other visitors to see.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, here's the link:  <a href="http://lazarus.carbonize.co.uk" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://lazarus.carbonize.co.uk</a></td>
